{"tid":1840884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［知乎]中了武汉肺炎是怎么的体验","createTime":"2020-01-25T04:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T05:27:08.000Z","uid":119507,"like":12,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"214edffe1f9273ccb9f6dff1325e26a9f031ca51","tid":1840884,"uid":119507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"万万怎不到 35岁的我竟了中了肺炎<br />\n见眼身边同行路者病死<br />\n而我虽然测出陈阳性反应<br />\n但我完全不觉得有任何异样<br />\n也许上帝早就选择了我让我幸存下去<br />\n<br />\n从武汉离逃到香港不一易事，赶上高铁最后一班车<br />\n浩浩荡荡踏上旅程<br />\n眼见身边的同胞突然休克，虽心有不忍，但也许是大自然的选择。<br />\n在铁路上死了好几个同胞，我会悼念他们，毕竟他们为自由与人权作出重大决定。<br />\n哪有国家会把自己的国民封在感染区，再围城坑杀。<br />\n我想只有共产党才会这样冷血。<br />\n没关系吧，我当年早已取得香港身份证，若干年后竟然可以大派用场。<br />\n<br />\n而然香港医疗是首屈一指的，入院时不需要预缴费用，虽然我现在没有任何病发的现象，但不排除日后的路，看过医生比较好。<br />\n<br />\n一个有香港身分证的中国人上"},{"pid":"87e2927bde026020b6766cb927fdd53d60a7526c","tid":1840884,"uid":182061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"466726167902bc8fa53359896fa062f06f7b2bd2","tid":1840884,"uid":49336,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街了"},{"pid":"d2ceaa31ba938291775b64d0546f24f9f13f969a","tid":1840884,"uid":126621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"政府不封關不作為<br />\n讓武漢病毒入侵香港<br />\n病毒持有者唔發燒，過關體檢check唔到<br />\n唔封關根本係謀殺香港人<br />\n<br />\n醫護界作為唯一能議價的人<br />\n卻認為罷工乜乜乜，責任攬上自己到<br />\n醫護不作為如同站在政府的一方<br />\n真係枉為人，我呸。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">下面兩條片講病毒唔會發燒，過幾日就死</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/5l7bf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F5l7bf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=b7790cf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/5l7bf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/t7d44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ft7d44&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=c9914355\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/t7d44</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片係專家分析<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有兩種冠狀病毒</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=3ce0629b\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYS7rf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYS7rf7.png&h=fa7cecd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">醫護界唔罷工，下場一定無好結果<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGJ6GOH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGJ6GOH.png&h=7d1d1de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/wmdyz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fwmdyz&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=62b6b9ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/wmdyz</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/bflau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fbflau&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=76af7c6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/bflau</a>"},{"pid":"83a652fa9450907d17570ac2cf136286e9655116","tid":1840884,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"b730b26b0e3cd08c02e19f32d1a767c049e4cb0f","tid":1840884,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"source？"},{"pid":"8ea3c77aa97c1e510922649826c30e2fec8d4adc","tid":1840884,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:56:19.000Z","msg":"link? or 9up?"},{"pid":"678f9a492af6418dfd835cc91921d2b79930b77e","tid":1840884,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"潮文黎咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2316540bd527d291efd66e848e0544a28b194f4","tid":1840884,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0aa0d728b5843a5080363565e4f0de521006994","tid":1840884,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:57:02.000Z","msg":"新潮文誕生"},{"pid":"39260c92d78a734f6a451c6c4cee4ace7bf80e17","tid":1840884,"uid":157516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"講故台？"},{"pid":"bfecc9315f01d29036db2ec9cab48f3641a0c04f","tid":1840884,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"個個淨係識po微博啲評論上黎，然後就笑9人，完全冇人討論點先可以令香港封閉邊境。<br />\n<br />\n你話醫護罷工就得？全民三罷呀！唔好將個責任推哂落醫護人員到，怪佢地唔罷工。咁耐以來，我地都係齊上齊落，依家香港生死存亡之際，我地更應該團結一致，一起對抗肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n1.立刻組織全民三罷<br />\n2.聯合十八區區議員，正式宣布香港進入緊急狀態<br />\n3.宣布全港學校停課<br />\n4.要求民陣組織遊行至高鐵<br />\n5.加強地區性消毒及衛生清潔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己香港自己救，我地唔可以再抱住隔岸觀火的態度面對肺炎，依個病毒已經殺到埋身！<br />\n<br />\n我地要同時間競賽！唔可以再拖落去！！！<br />\n<br />\n全民三罷，香港封關！！"},{"pid":"81461fa33608a8a87dcd7f8b2f73e2940472fe60","tid":1840884,"uid":198952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:57:47.000Z","msg":"11/10"},{"pid":"dda4f903b266087b67229e3d7e9174a5fdd00944","tid":1840884,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"466726167902bc8fa53359896fa062f06f7b2bd2","tid":1840884,"uid":49336,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000